description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby discuss the Cowboys’ “State of the Team” address at the opening of training camp in Oxnard, CA. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
